---
title: Spanish Style Chicken and Chorizo Rice with Peas
description: Our Spanish Style Chorizo Rice is just like a risotto, but with the flavours of Spain. This one's a simplified version of the traditional risotto or baked rice, baking in the oven instead to absorb all the stock and flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W36_UK_G4553-18484-7_Main_V2_low-ae05a3aa.jpg
